episodes.title: Meditation retreat turned out to be a cult
episodes.description:
Hi and welcome to my video, today i sit down and talk about an experience i had back in 2018 where i signed up for a meditation retreat but it turned out to be a cult (or at least that what it looked like). 

I keep saying 'i almost joined a cult, which i obviously didnt but what I meant to say was that 'the meditation retreat turned out to be a cult' lol.







#cult #cultstory #ukcults #horror #horrorchannel #midnighthorrorclub #crime
